lead_paragraph: Five soldiers had been killed and 12 wounded in fighting in the separatist east, casting further doubt on the prospects for a months-old cease-fire that has never fully taken hold.

abstract: Ukrainian military reports that five soldiers killed and 12 wounded in fighting in separatist territories, further dimming hopes that months-old cease-fire will take hold.
